description.narrative: (USAID Southern Africa Regional): Technical Support to PEPFAR Program in Southern Africa (TSP) provides technical assistance (TA) to USAID bilateral missions and other operating units in southern Africa to achieve the UNAIDS fast track targets and epidemic control within their HIV/AIDS programs. ..TSP focuses on the following three objectives:. TA to improve clinical outcomes of PEFAR programs in the region Improve and expand pediatric and adolescent HIV/AIDS treatment services in the regionIn close cooperation with USAID bilateral missions and other operating units, implement PEPFAR programs through specific buy-insBenefiting Countries: Botswana, Mozambique, Zimbabwe, Namibia, South Africa, Angola
